snippet.title: [MH Playthrough] Trouble Witches Origin - Episode 1 Daughters of Amalgam - (PC)
snippet.description:
A (very bad attempt) at a playthrough of Trouble Witches.

I was uber tired at the time of recording, and didn't feel like giving up half way, so in the second half of the game, be prepared to see me die TONS. Thanks god I didn't need to pay quarters per continue...
